Template: tt-local-generator/hf-token
Type: password
Default:
Description: HuggingFace access token (optional for Wan2.2-T2V)
 The Wan2.2-T2V-A14B model (~118 GB) is publicly available on HuggingFace
 without a license gate.
 .
 A HuggingFace token can be provided to avoid API rate limits during
 download. Leave blank to download anonymously.
 .
 Your token is used once and immediately discarded — it is not stored by
 this package. To skip providing a token, just press Enter.
